&lt;li&gt;Preparing, reviewing, and submitting KYC documentation packages, including corporate, ownership, and financial information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating with Compliance, Legal, Tax, Treasury, and other internal stakeholders to gather and validate information required for due diligence activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responding to ongoing due diligence enquiries and ensuring accurate, complete, and timely delivery of information to counterparties.&lt;/li&gt;
