&lt;li&gt;Ensuring compliance with AML, KYC, regulatory, and internal policy requirements while maintaining appropriate audit trails and supporting documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying and escalating risks, discrepancies, or complex issues related to due diligence, banking relationships, or account structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting internal audits, regulatory reviews, and continuous improvement initiatives by maintaining documentation, enhancing processes, and improving the efficiency of KYC and banking governance activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
